                ________________________________________________________

                | Design          |  Value           |                  |

                |  Property       |                  |                  |

                |_________________|__________________|__________________|

                | Design Name     |  dsp_test        |                  |

                |_________________|__________________|__________________|

                |                 |  MAX             |  MIN             |

                |_________________|__________________|__________________|

                | Operating       |  tdsp_core/%NOM_ |   tdsp_core/%NOM |

                |  Condition Name |  PVT             |  _PVT            |

                |_________________|__________________|__________________|

                | Process         |  1.000           |   1.000          |

                |_________________|__________________|__________________|

                | Voltage         |  1.800           |   1.800          |

                |_________________|__________________|__________________|

                | Temperature     |  25.000          |   25.000         |

                |_________________|__________________|__________________|

                | Tree Type       |  worst_case      |   worst_case     |

                |_________________|__________________|__________________|

              Max Transition
                NA

              Min Transition
                NA

              Max Capacitance
                NA

              Min Capacitance
                NA

              Max Fanout
                NA

                Min Fanout" NA

